# Session 013 – Moment

## Goal

Define the Moment concept.

---

## Decisions

Moments represent meaningful experiences worth remembering.

Moments may be created automatically by DailyPaws or manually by the family.

Moments belong to one of four categories:

- Connection
- Achievement
- Discovery
- Joy

Moments contribute to the family's Journey.

